Siconos API (C/C++)
===================

Different versions on test

* Doxygen only (a doxygen conf + run doxygen, html mode)
* Exhale : use conf.py (sphinx) to handle doxygen run (xml outputs + rst generations from those outputs) and sphinx build
* Doxyrest : same results as exhale but not as convenient as exhale. I use it to generate rst files from \page inputs in doxygen and that's it.

  
